UI.textUI

Class ScreenExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • UI.textUI.ScreenExecutor

  • public class ScreenExecutor
extends java.lang.Object
    A Screen Executor execute a queue of Screen one by one. A screen is rendered until it indicates it doesn't have next.
